<div class="riskr-mission">
  <div class="riskr-mission__inner page-width">
    <div class="riskr-mission__label">Our Mission</div>
    <div class="riskr-mission__body">
      <h2 class="riskr-mission__headline">Driving Impact at Scale.<br>One Shirt at a Time.</h2>
      <div class="riskr-mission__copy">
        <p>At Riskr, we believe that meaningful disruption begins with what you wear to the all-hands meeting.</p>
        <p>Our garments are engineered to communicate alignment, signal bandwidth, and facilitate the kind of low-friction stakeholder engagement that moves the needle on cross-functional deliverables.</p>
        <p>This is not a clothing company. This is a human capital optimization platform that happens to sell shirts.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .riskr-mission {
    background: #f5f5f5;
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .riskr-mission__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .riskr-mission__label {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #00000060;
    padding-top: 8px;
  }

  .riskr-mission__headline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
  }

  .riskr-mission__copy p {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #00000099;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .riskr-mission__copy p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .riskr-mission {
      padding: 64px 0;
    }

    .riskr-mission__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Riskr Mission",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "riskr-mission-section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Riskr Mission"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
